title: Sheikh Mohammed unveils DH1 billion campaign to fight hunger this Ramadan
summary_full: Dubai's Ruler has launched the 'Edge of Life' campaign to combat child hunger, aiming to save five million children under five from malnutrition-related deaths. This initiative, coinciding with Ramadan, seeks to raise AED1 billion for vital programs.
